    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/9fb49c95ee74a9bf2f9660fb0e9c8ef1.poster.avif?t=1745598538\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/9fb49c95ee74a9bf2f9660fb0e9c8ef1.webm?t=1745598538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/9fb49c95ee74a9bf2f9660fb0e9c8ef1.mp4?t=1745598538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Travel throughout the galaxy, finding new and interesting things in each star system. Pilot your space ship in star systems and land on the 11 different fully procedural planets. Click on planets to find information on the planets before you land, some require special gear. Warp to the shop planet to sell and buy useful items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/ade9ec3ce33e38066c29663d7af55c86.poster.avif?t=1745598538\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/ade9ec3ce33e38066c29663d7af55c86.webm?t=1745598538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/ade9ec3ce33e38066c29663d7af55c86.mp4?t=1745598538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Find a planet and make it yours. Use the ability to bookmark planets to be able to travel back to your planet no matter where you are in the galaxy. Build with almost 300 different blocks and items. Farm crops and sell them to become the richest person in the galaxy. Beware off the hostile inhabitants of these worlds, they will put up a fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/4a6217793f6ea4d53b46f2faf9f36dae.poster.avif?t=1745598538\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/4a6217793f6ea4d53b46f2faf9f36dae.webm?t=1745598538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208770/extras/4a6217793f6ea4d53b46f2faf9f36dae.mp4?t=1745598538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover the hidden secrets of the galaxy. Conquer multiple different procedurally generated dungeons, and claim the rewards. Upgrade your weapons and armor to survive these challenges. Locate the endgame planet and destroy the boss.",
